flowchart TD
    MAIL_ROUTER[BTS public mail router]
    RELAY[POST /inbound-email/relay]
    ACTION_MAILBOX[Action Mailbox inbound email]
    RESOLVE[InboundEmailResolutionService]
    MESSAGE[InboundEmailMessage encrypted record]
    MAIL_SCAN[MailScreeningService]
    ORCHESTRATOR[Content-security orchestrator runner]
    HOLD[Hold for review]
    ROUTE[Route to CE target]
    MEMBERSHIP[Membership request creation]

    UPLOAD[Active Storage upload]
    SUBJECT[ContentSecurity::Subject]
    SYNC[AttachmentSubjectSync]
    BLOB_POLICY[BlobAccessPolicy]
    BLOB_PROXY[CE blob proxy routes]
    PRIVATE[Pending/private until released]
    RELEASED[Released attachment serving]

    RICH_TEXT[Action Text content]
    VALIDATE[Reject unsupported embeds]
    RICH_SYNC[RichTextSubjectSync]
    FILTER[RichTextAttachmentFilter]
    RENDER[Rendered rich text]

    MAIL_ROUTER --> RELAY
    RELAY --> ACTION_MAILBOX
    ACTION_MAILBOX --> RESOLVE
    RESOLVE --> MESSAGE
    MESSAGE --> MAIL_SCAN
    MAIL_SCAN --> ORCHESTRATOR
    ORCHESTRATOR -->|clean or monitor| ROUTE
    ORCHESTRATOR -->|review_required restricted quarantined blocked| HOLD
    ROUTE --> MEMBERSHIP

    UPLOAD --> SUBJECT
    UPLOAD --> SYNC
    SYNC --> SUBJECT
    SUBJECT --> BLOB_POLICY
    BLOB_POLICY -->|not releasable| PRIVATE
    BLOB_POLICY -->|releasable| BLOB_PROXY
    BLOB_PROXY --> RELEASED

    RICH_TEXT --> VALIDATE
    VALIDATE --> RICH_SYNC
    RICH_SYNC --> SUBJECT
    SUBJECT --> FILTER
    FILTER --> RENDER

    classDef ingress fill:#e3f2fd
    classDef security fill:#fff3e0
    classDef hold fill:#ffebee
    classDef release fill:#e8f5e8

    class MAIL_ROUTER,RELAY,ACTION_MAILBOX,RESOLVE,MESSAGE,UPLOAD,RICH_TEXT ingress
    class MAIL_SCAN,ORCHESTRATOR,SUBJECT,SYNC,BLOB_POLICY,VALIDATE,RICH_SYNC,FILTER security
    class HOLD,PRIVATE hold
    class ROUTE,MEMBERSHIP,BLOB_PROXY,RELEASED,RENDER release
